text: Verzasca is a municipality of the district Locarno in the canton of Ticino in Switzerland. On 17 October 2020 the former municipalities of Brione (Verzasca), Corippo, Frasco, Sonogno and Vogorno merged to form the new municipality of Verzasca. == References == Category:2020 establishments in Switzerland
title: Verzasca, Switzerland
